---
import PageLayout from '../components/templates/PageLayout.astro';

const sections = [
  {
    title: 'Introduction',
    body:
      'This Privacy Policy describes how Ikeda Senchado ("we", "our") collects, uses, and protects information when you visit our online store or interact with our services. We are committed to handling your data with the same patience and care we bring to our tea. By using our website, you agree to the practices described in this document. We may revise this policy from time to time, and any updates will be posted on this page with a new effective date.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Information We Collect',
    body:
      'We collect information you provide directly, such as your name, shipping address, email, and payment details when you place an order. We also collect technical information automatically, including your IP address, browser type, and pages visited, to help us understand how our site is used. If you contact us for support, we keep a record of that correspondence so we can serve you better. We do not knowingly collect information from anyone under the age of 16.',
  },
  {
    title: 'How We Use Information',
    body:
      'We use the information we collect to fulfill orders, deliver your tea, process payments, and respond to your questions. We may also use it to send order confirmations, shipping updates, and, if you opt in, occasional newsletters from Ikeda Senchado. Aggregated, anonymized data helps us refine our products and improve the website experience. We never sell your personal information.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Cookies',
    body:
      'Our website uses cookies and similar technologies to keep your cart contents, remember preferences, and gather analytics about site performance. You may disable cookies in your browser settings, though some parts of the site (such as checkout) rely on them and may not function correctly without them. We use a small number of trusted third-party analytics providers, each bound by their own privacy commitments.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Third-Party Sharing',
    body:
      'We share information only with service providers who help us operate our business, such as payment processors, shipping carriers, and email platforms. These partners receive only the information required to perform their function and are contractually bound to protect it. We may disclose information when required by law or to protect the rights and safety of Ikeda Senchado, our customers, or others.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Your Rights',
    body:
      'You have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of the personal information we hold about you. You may also withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time by following the unsubscribe link in any email or contacting us directly. Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have additional rights under applicable data protection laws, which we will honor in accordance with those laws.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Contact',
    body:
      'If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your information, please reach out to us at privacy@ikedasenchado.com or through our contact page. We aim to respond to every inquiry within five business days.',
  },
];
---

<PageLayout title="Privacy Policy | Ikeda Senchado">
  <div class="pt-48 pb-32 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="mb-24 text-center">
      <p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-outline mb-4 uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">Legal Information</p>
      <h1 class="font-h1 text-h1 text-primary mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-primary mx-auto"></div>
    </header>

    <!-- Sections -->
    <section class="space-y-0">
      {
        sections.map((s) => (
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 border-b border-neutral-100 py-10 gap-6">
            <div class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-outline uppercase md:pt-1">{s.title}</div>
            <div class="md:col-span-2 mt-2 md:mt-0 font-body-md text-body-md text-primary leading-relaxed">
              {s.body}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </section>

    <!-- Visual Element -->
    <div class="mt-32 relative h-96 w-full bg-surface">
      <img
        alt=""
        class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-20"
        src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA_MX2CRtCZ14rXFwK8pPvymQN3VbBIQ6mWjEP1fENG5noqvFUB2fe2gGzAQyjhuhjLRHyHBlhdp1H2Ur9wWn38VohnhVIGk0HtIRmgg9Xt0yralhoGyVY3nb8_NQdkSqIOi73x4s7iPK0K60W-XVwkeCvyLyxSr_FSaZbEvcGmay5DHjKiyfZMLPDaD7So0RoPV_Pcz1thIUvFkGsOLlLQUPlcr621QPe6MttIfEg6jxw7BvijZEG76oKRn_ZbVq9IbRgFrtYJ5n8"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
        <p class="font-serif italic text-h3 text-neutral-300">Privacy, like a quiet cup.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
